                            <comment id="14494077" author="ashish singhi" created="Tue, 14 Apr 2015 13:03:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch lgtm.&lt;br/&gt;
This should go only in branch-1.&lt;br/&gt;
In master branch we are updating the region count in the namespace quota only on successful merge.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14494087" author="yuzhihong@gmail.com" created="Tue, 14 Apr 2015 13:12:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here is an alternate solution.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;regionStateListener.onRegionMerged() is called only when merge succeeds. This aligns with the behavior in master branch so that we don&apos;t introduce new callback in RegionStateListener&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I can adjust the subject of this JIRA if v2 is deemed better.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14494128" author="ashish singhi" created="Tue, 14 Apr 2015 13:41:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;v2 looks much better.&lt;br/&gt;
